An samu karuwar yawan kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) a Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da kuma Burtaniya daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Cunkoson cututtukan cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) ya nuna irin wannan yanayin a tsakanin ƙasashen Tarayyar Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Burtaniya wanda ke tabbatar da cewa duk da cewa akwai matakai daban-daban dangane da ƙasa, cutar ta COVID-19 tana ci gaba cikin sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Dangane da ilimin da aka samu daga Italiya, dole ne ƙasar, asibitoci da na'urorin kulawa mai mahimmanci su haɓaka shirye-shirye don saurin haɓaka marasa lafiya da ke fama da COVID-19 waɗanda ke buƙatar kulawa ta musamman da kulawa mai mahimmanci.
An ba da rahoton wani mummunan yanayin cutar sankarar bargo a Wuhan, lardin Hubei na kasar Sin, a ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019.
A ranar 9 ga Janairu, 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafin Cututtuka ta China ta ba da sanarwar cewa sabon coronavirus a matsayin mai aiki yanzu ana kiransa da cutar coronavirus mai saurin numfashi mai saurin cuta 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Saboda haka, cutar da ke haifar da SARS-CoV-2 an sanya mata sunan cutar coronavirus (COVID-19).
Bayanai na yau da kullun sun nuna cewa kashi 80% na waɗanda ke da COVID-19 suna da ƙananan cututtuka, wato, kamuwa da numfashi tare da ko ba tare da cutar huhu ba, kuma mafi yawansu sun warke.
A cikin kashi 14 cikin ɗari na waɗanda suka kamu, COVID-19 ya zama mafi tsanani wanda ke buƙatar asibiti, yayin da kashi 6 cikin ɗari suka kamu da rashin lafiya mai tsanani wanda ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani.
Yawan mutuwar marasa lafiya da ke asibiti saboda COVID-19 ya kai kusan kashi 4 cikin dari.
A cikin wannan binciken, mun bincika yanayin ƙaruwar COVID-19 a kowace Tarayyar Turai / Ƙasar Tattalin Arzikin Turai (EU/EEA) da Burtaniya (UK) kuma mun kwatanta su da lardin Hubei na China.
Mun kuma gwada adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 a ƙasashen EU/EEA da Burtaniya da kuma Italiya tsakanin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Al'amuran COVID-19 a ƙasashen EU/EEA da kuma Birtaniya
COVID-19 ya ci gaba da yaduwa a geographical, bayan China, kuma yanayin COVID-19 a sauran yankuna na duniya yanzu yana bin wannan ƙasar.
Darakta Janar na Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba a ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020.
A cikin fitowar 5 ga Maris na EuroSurveillance 2020, Spiteri da abokansa sun ba da rahoton farkon mutanen Turai da aka tabbatar da cutar COVID-19 bisa ga ma'anar yanayin WHO.
A EU/EEA, Faransa ta sanar da farkon mutane uku da suka tabbatar da cutar a ranar 24 ga Janairu, 2020, a cikin mutanen da suka dawo daga Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, COVID-19 ya bayyana a duk ƙasashe 30 na EU/EEA da Burtaniya, tare da rahoton mutum 39,768 da mutuwar 1,727 tun daga ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, tare da 17,750 da mutuwar 1,441 a Italiya kadai.
Samun adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 da kuma yawan adadin su
Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC) tana ba da rahoton ƙididdigar COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa a duniya, wanda aka samo daga ma'aikatun kiwon lafiya na ƙasashe, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na ƙasa da na yanki, da kuma tushen gwamnati kamar WHO, wanda aka sabunta a 8:00 na safe kowace rana.
An yi amfani da wannan bayanan don kimanta yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU / EEA da Burtaniya da kuma kwatanta shi da abin da ya faru a Italiya.
A matsayin wakili na barkewar cutar COVID-19, mun ƙidaya gajerun kwanaki 14 na COVID-19, ta haka ne la'akari da yanayin COVID-19 a kowace EU/EEA da Burtaniya daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Mun kuma gabatar da adadi mai yawa na lamuran da aka rubuta a kowace ƙasa har zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020 da karfe 8:00 na safe, kuma mun gwada shi da adadin waɗanda suka kamu da cutar a Italiya daga 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Yanayin COVID-19 a ƙasashen EU/EEA da Burtaniya
Yanayin kwanan nan na COVID-19 na kwanaki 14 a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da Burtaniya ya bi yanayin lardin Hubei (China) gaba ɗaya (Hoto 1).
Ga EU/EEA da Burtaniya gabaɗaya, adadin COVID-19 ya fara ƙaruwa a kusa da 21 ga Fabrairu, sannan ya ƙaru sosai a kusa da 28 ga Fabrairu, 2020 (Supplementary Material).
Wannan ya samo asali ne daga saurin karuwar adadin masu kamuwa da cutar a Italiya, amma duk sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA da Burtaniya sun nuna irin wannan ci gaban a cikin ƙaruwar COVID-19 (kayan aiki).
Hoto na 2 ya nuna kwatancen lambobi a Italiya da kuma adadin adadin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK na 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Ya kamata a lura cewa, a ranar 15 ga Maris, da karfe 8:00 na safe, sauran ƙasashe 15 na EU/EEA da Burtaniya sun riga sun ba da rahoton adadin waɗanda za a iya kwatanta su da Italiya a cikin makonni 3 ko ƙasa da haka.
Sakamakonmu ya nuna cewa adadin mutanen da aka sani da cutar COVID-19 na ƙaruwa cikin sauri a EU/EEA da kuma Burtaniya.
Yanayin da ake gani a cikin tarin COVID-19 yana nuna cewa annobar tana ci gaba da sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Wannan duk da cewa ƙasashe suna cikin matakai daban-daban, duk da bambancin halayen lafiyar jama'a na ƙasa, kuma duk da cewa ƙasashe na iya samun ma'anoni daban-daban na waɗanda ke kamuwa da cuta da kuma ka'idoji daban-daban don zaɓin marasa lafiya waɗanda dole ne a gwada su don tabbatar da COVID-19, gami da gwajin kamawa.
A farkon watan Maris na 2020, likitoci a yankunan da ke fama da cutar a Italiya sun bayyana halin da ake ciki inda kashi 10% na masu cutar COVID-19 ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani, kuma kafofin watsa labarai sun nuna cewa asibitoci da na'urorin kulawa mai tsanani a waɗannan yankuna sun riga sun kai iyakar ƙarfin su.
Bayanai game da shigar da masu cutar COVID-19 a asibiti da / ko sashen kulawa mai tsanani a halin yanzu ana samun su ne kawai a kashi 6% da 1% na masu cutar a matakin EU / EEA, bi da bi (ba a nuna bayanan ba).
