Idan ba su yi haka ba, akwai yiwuwar cewa tsarin kiwon lafiya a wasu ƙasashen EU/EEA zai fuskanci karuwar adadin marasa lafiya da ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani a cikin kwanaki da makonni masu zuwa.
