Baya ga abubuwan da ke tattare da kayan shafawa da kuma kare fata, shirye-shiryen da aka ƙera na iya ƙunsar acid (acetic acid, ascorbic acid, lactic acid), antibacterially active benzoic acid, da ƙarin masu sanyaya fata (alovera, bitamin, methanol, tsire-tsire na shuka) a matsayin masu daidaita pH. Wani cikakken bincike na Jami'ar Oregon School of Public Health ya nuna cewa sabulu na yau da kullun kamar su Trakhlovan sun hada da sabulun anti-bacterial don hana cututtuka da cire kwayoyin cuta daga hannu.
