A ƙarshen shekarun 1990 da farkon ƙarni na 21, kayan aikin tsabtace hannu na giya (wanda aka fi sani da tushen giya, antiseptic hand rub, ko kuma hand sanitizer) sun fara samun shahara.
Don sauƙin amfani da rage tasirin busar da giya, an yi galibi ne bisa isopropyl alcohol ko ethanol wanda aka shirya tare da carbomer (polymer na acrylic acid) ko humicant kamar su ruwa ko kuma a cikin kumfa tare da kayan kauri kamar glycerin.
Haɗa hydrogen-peroxide mai haɗuwa yana ƙara haɓaka ayyukan antimicrobial. Hannun tsabtace hannu yana da ƙarancin 60 zuwa 95% na giya wanda ke da tasiri wajen kashe ƙwayoyin cuta.
