Addinai suna ba da umarnin wanke hannu don dalilai na kiwon lafiya da na alama. Wanke hannu na alama, amfani da ruwa / ruwa don wanke hannu amma ba sabulu ba, wani ɓangare ne na al'adun addini na wanke hannu wanda ke nuna yawancin addinai, gami da Baha'i, Hindu, Tewilah da Netilat Yadaim a addinin Yahudanci, Lavobo a cikin Kristanci da Ozu a cikin Musulunci. Addinai suna ba da umarnin wanke hannu mai kyau bayan yin wasu ayyuka.
A addinin Hindu, Yahudanci da Musulunci wanke hannu bayan amfani da bayan gida yana da muhimmanci.
Kuma, wanke hannu kafin da kuma bayan kowane abinci wajibi ne a addinin Hindu, Buddha, Sikh, Yahudanci da Musulunci.
Gudanar da haɗarin aiki don COVID-19
Kula da haɗarin aiki don COVID-19 shine aiwatar da hanyoyin lafiya da kiwon lafiya na aiki don sarrafa haɗarin don hana cutar coronavirus na 2019 (COVID-19).
Kulawa mai kyau na haɗari a wurin aiki ya dogara da wurin aiki da aikin da ake yi, da kimanta haɗarin tushen haɗari, tsananin cutar a cikin al'umma, da kuma abubuwan haɗarin ma'aikata na musamman waɗanda ke da haɗarin kamuwa da COVID-19.
A cewar Hukumar Kula da Lafiya da Lafiya ta Amurka (OSHA), ayyukan da ke da ƙananan haɗari suna ɗaukar mafi ƙarancin aiki tare da jama'a da sauran abokan aiki, wanda ke ba da shawarar matakan hana kamuwa da cuta, gami da wanke hannu, ƙarfafa ma'aikata su zauna a gida idan suna rashin lafiya, ladabi na numfashi, da tsabtace aiki na yau da kullun da kuma tsabtace yanayin aiki.
Ayyukan da ke da matsakaicin haɗarin haɗari sun haɗa da ayyukan da ba a san ko ana zargin cewa akwai COVID-19 ba, amma wuraren kasuwancin suna buƙatar haɗuwa sosai ko kusanci da mutanen da ke iya kamuwa da cutar saboda cutar da ke yaduwa a cikin jama'a ko kuma tafiya ta duniya.
Wannan ya haɗa da ma'aikata da suke da alaƙa da jama'a, kamar su makarantu, wuraren aiki masu yawan jama'a, da kuma wuraren sayar da kayayyaki masu yawan jama'a.
Baya ga matakan rigakafin farko, tsarin kula da haɗari ga wannan rukunin ya haɗa da samun iska mai ƙarfi ta amfani da matattarar iska, masu tsaron sneez, da kuma samar da kayan kariya na mutum lokacin da suka fuskanci mutumin da ke da cutar COVID-19.
OSHA ta ce ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya da ma'aikatan jana'iza suna da haɗarin haɗuwa da waɗanda ke da tabbacin ko kuma waɗanda ake zargi da cutar COVID-19. Wannan haɗarin ya ƙaru idan ma'aikatan sun yi amfani da hanyoyin samar da aerosol ko kuma sun tattara ko kuma sarrafa samfuran waɗanda ke da tabbacin ko kuma waɗanda ake zargi da cutar COVID-19.
Hanyoyin da za a iya amfani da su wajen hana haɗari ga ma'aikata sun haɗa da sarrafa injiniya kamar su ɗakunan iska masu matsin lamba, da kuma kayan kariya na mutum da suka dace da aikin.
Cutar COVID-19 na iya haifar da tasiri mai yawa a wuraren aiki.
Ma'aikata na iya yin rashin aiki saboda rashin lafiya, don kula da wasu, ko kuma don tsoron haɗuwa.
Abubuwan da ake buƙata da kuma hanyar da ake sayen waɗannan kayayyakin (kamar sayayya a lokacin da ba a cika aiki ba ko ta hanyar isarwa ko sabis na tuki-ta hanyar (saya ba tare da sauka daga mota ba), duka suna iya canza yanayin kasuwanci.
A ƙarshe, jigilar kaya daga yankuna masu tasirin COVID-19 na iya zama mai rikitarwa. Za'a iya amfani da shirin shiri da amsa cutar mai yaduwa don jagorantar matakan kariya.
Shirye-shiryen suna magance matakan haɗari da ke tattare da wuraren aiki da ayyuka daban-daban, gami da tushen haɗari, abubuwan haɗari daga gida da kuma al'umma, da abubuwan haɗarin mutum na ma'aikata kamar tsufa ko cututtukan likita na yau da kullun.
Sun kuma bayyana matakan da ake buƙata don magance waɗannan haɗarin da kuma shirye-shiryen da za a iya yi don yanayin da zai iya tasowa sakamakon barkewar cutar.
Shirye-shiryen cututtukan cututtuka da shirye-shiryen amsawa na iya zama batun shawarwarin ƙasa ko na ƙasa.
Manufofin amsawa ga barkewar cutar sun haɗa da rage kamuwa da cuta a cikin ma'aikata, kare mutanen da ke cikin haɗarin haɗarin haɗarin rashin lafiya, kiyaye ayyukan kasuwanci, da rage tasirin tasirin su ga sauran ƙungiyoyi a cikin sarkar samar da su.
Matsayin cutar a cikin al'umma inda kasuwancin yake yana shafar yadda ake amsawa.
Tsarin tsari na kula da haɗari tsari ne da aka yi amfani da shi sosai wajen kula da lafiyar sana'a da lafiya.
Inda ba za a iya kawar da haɗarin COVID-19 ba, mafi ingantattun matakan sarrafawa sune sarrafa injiniya, sannan sarrafawa, kuma a ƙarshe kayan kariya na mutum.
Gudanarwa na injiniya ya ƙunshi ware ma'aikata daga haɗarin aiki ba tare da dogaro da halayen ma'aikata ba, kuma yana iya zama mafi kyawun mafita don aiwatarwa.
Dokokin gudanarwa su ne canje-canje a manufofin aiki ko hanyoyin da ke bukatar aiki daga ma'aikaci ko mai aiki.
Kayan kariya na mutum (PPE) ana ganin ba su da tasiri fiye da na injiniya da na gudanarwa, amma yana iya taimakawa wajen hana wasu fallasa.
Za a zaɓi duk PPE bisa ga haɗarin ma'aikaci, a dace da shi yadda ya dace (kamar masu numfashi), a ci gaba da sawa yadda ya kamata, a bincika, a kula da kuma maye gurbinsa a kai a kai, kuma a buɗe shi, a tsabtace shi, kuma a adana shi ko a watsar da shi don kauce wa gurɓata.
Aikin da ke da ƙananan haɗari na haɗari yana da iyakancewar haɗuwa da jama'a da sauran abokan aiki, in ji Hukumar Kula da Lafiya da Lafiya ta Amurka (OSHA).
Matakan rigakafin kamuwa da cuta da aka ba da shawarar ga duk wuraren aiki sun haɗa da wanke hannu da kyau da kuma sau da yawa, ƙarfafa ma'aikata su zauna a gida idan suna rashin lafiya, samar da ladabi na numfashi, gami da rufe fuska yayin tari da tari, samar da kayan aiki da kwandon shara, kasancewa a shirye don sadarwa ta waya ko sauyawa a wasu lokuta na rana idan ya cancanta, hana ma'aikata amfani da kayan aikin wasu, da kiyaye tsabtace yanayi da tsabtace yanayi.
Mataki na farko da ya kamata a ɗauka don kiyaye ma'aikata, abokan ciniki, masu neman aiki da sauran mutane a wuraren aiki shine ganowa da ware mutanen da ke da cutar.
Ma'aikatan da ke da alamun cututtukan numfashi na yau da kullun, Cibiyoyin Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafi na Amurka suna ba da shawarar su zauna a gida har sai sun sami nutsuwa daga zazzabi, alamun zazzabi, da sauran alamun cutar aƙalla awanni 24 ba tare da amfani da magungunan rage zazzabi ko wasu magungunan canza alamun ba, kuma ya kamata a sassauta manufofin hutun rashin lafiya, wanda ke ba ma'aikata damar zama a gida don kula da wani dangin da ke rashin lafiya, kuma ma'aikata su san waɗannan manufofin.
A cewar OSHA, ayyukan da ke da matsakaicin haɗarin haɗari sun haɗa da ayyukan da ba a san ko ana zargin cewa akwai COVID-19 ba, amma yana buƙatar haɗuwa ta kai tsaye ko kusa da mutane waɗanda ke da cutar SARS-CoV-2 a tsakanin ƙafa shida (1.8 m) saboda cutar da ke yaduwa a cikin jama'a a wuraren kasuwanci ko kuma tafiya ta duniya kwanan nan zuwa wani wuri inda COVID-19 ya yadu.
Ayyukan sarrafawa na ma'aikata da ke da alaƙa da jama'a sun haɗa da ƙarfafa marasa lafiya su kasance a gida, maye gurbin hulɗa ta fuska da fuska ta hanyar na'urori na kama-da-wane, gabatar da sauye-sauye na musamman don COVID-19, samar da matakan kiyayewa na yau da kullun a wuraren aiki, ba da horo ga ma'aikata game da yanayin da ke tattare da COVID-19, hana su yin amfani da kayan aiki na yau da kullun, ba da horo ga ma'aikata da kuma masu amfani da wuraren aiki, ba da horo ga masu amfani da wuraren aiki game da yadda za su iya dogara da yanayin da ke tattare da COVID-19, da kuma yadda za a magance matsalolin COVID-19, da kuma samar da wasu hanyoyin kiyayewa na yau da kullun ga ma'aikata da kuma ma'aikatan da ke amfani da kayan aikin kiyayewa na yau da kullun, da kuma samar da horo ga masu amfani da wuraren aiki game da yadda za su iya magance COVID-19.
A wasu lokuta, ma'aikatan da ke cikin wannan rukunin haɗarin suna buƙatar yin amfani da na'urar numfashi.
Idan mutum ya kamu da rashin lafiya a cikin jirgin, matakan da suka dace don kare ma'aikata da sauran fasinjoji sun haɗa da ware mutum mai rashin lafiya daga sauran mutane a nisan ƙafa 6, sanya wani memba na ma'aikata don kula da mutumin da ke fama da rashin lafiya, da kuma ba wa mutumin da ke fama da rashin lafiya abin rufe fuska ko kuma ya nemi mutumin da ke fama da rashin lafiya ya rufe bakinsa da hanci da nama yayin hancinsa ko tari.
Ya kamata ma'aikatan jirgin su sanya safofin hannu na likita lokacin amsa kiran matafiyi mara lafiya ko kuma lokacin da suka taɓa ruwan jiki ko ɓangarorin da ke iya gurɓata su, kuma ya kamata su yi amfani da ƙarin kayan kariya na sirri idan matafiyin mara lafiya yana da zazzabi, ciwon tari ko numfashi.
Ya kamata a zubar da safofin hannu da sauran abubuwan zubarwa a cikin jakar haɗarin halittu, sannan a tsabtace da kuma tsabtace wuraren da ke da gurɓataccen abu. Don jiragen ruwa na kasuwanci, ciki har da jiragen ruwa da sauran jiragen ruwa, matakan haɗari sun haɗa da jinkirta tafiya mara lafiya, ware kanka, da kuma sanar da cibiyar kiwon lafiya ta jirgin idan wani ya nuna zazzabi ko wasu alamun bayyanar cututtuka yayin da yake cikin jirgin.
A matsayin manufa, ya kamata a bi da lafiyar a cikin ɗakin da aka keɓe. A cikin makarantu da wuraren kula da yara, CDC ta ba da shawarar rufewa na ɗan lokaci don tsabtace ko kuma kashe ƙwayoyin cuta idan wani mai cutar ya shiga cikin ginin makaranta, ba tare da la'akari da yadda cutar ke yaduwa a cikin jama'a ba.
Lokacin da cutar ta yi kadan zuwa matsakaici a cikin al'umma, ana iya aiwatar da dabarun nisantar zamantakewa, kamar soke tafiye-tafiye na filin, tarurruka da sauran manyan tarurruka, kamar karatun motsa jiki ko cin abinci a cikin cafeteria; ƙara tazarar tsakanin tebur, raba lokutan zuwa ofis da hutu, iyakance baƙi marasa mahimmanci, da amfani da keɓaɓɓiyar ofishin kiwon lafiya don yara masu alamun cutar mura.
Lokacin da cutar ta yadu a cikin al'ummomin gida, ana iya yin la'akari da ƙarin ɓarna a cikin makarantu don dabarun nisantar zamantakewa. CDC ta ɗauki haɗarin rashin lafiyar ma'aikatan tilasta bin doka waɗanda ke gudanar da ayyukan yau da kullun a matsayin ƙasa.
Jami'an tilasta bin doka waɗanda ke da alaƙa da mutanen da ke da tabbataccen ko ake zargin suna da COVID-19 ana ba da shawara su bi ƙa'idodin da ake ba da su ga masu fasahar likita na gaggawa, gami da kayan kariya na sirri.
Idan ma'aikata sun yi hulɗa ta kusa a lokacin da ake da damuwa, ya kamata a tsabtace su da kuma kashe kayan aikin su ta hanyar amfani da mai tsabtace gida ko shafawa kafin a sake amfani da su, kuma a bi hanyoyin sarrafa shaida don sarrafawa da kuma kawar da PPE da aka yi amfani da su.
OSHA ta sanya wasu ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya da na mutuwa a cikin manyan ko kuma masu haɗarin haɗari.
Ayyukan haɗarin haɗari sun haɗa da samar da kiwon lafiya, tallafi, ma'aikatan dakin gwaje-gwaje da ma'aikatan jigilar likita waɗanda suka haɗu da marasa lafiya waɗanda aka sani ko ake zargin suna da COVID-19.
Idan ma'aikata suna aiwatar da hanyoyin samar da aerosol, ko tattara ko motsa samfuran daga marasa lafiya da aka sani ko ake zargi da COVID-19, suna da babban haɗarin haɗuwa.
Hanyoyin samar da aerosol sun hada da shigar da bututu, hanyoyin fara coughing, bronchoscopy, wasu hanyoyin hakori da kuma daukar samfur ta hanyar shigar da gwaji ko kayan aiki.
Ayyukan haɗarin haɗari, haɗarin mutuwa sun haɗa da ma'aikatan da ke aiki a kan shirya gawawwakin mutanen da aka san ko ake zargin suna da COVID-19 a lokacin mutuwar; wannan ya zama haɗarin haɗari sosai idan sun yi autopsy. Ƙarin sarrafawar injiniya ga mutanen da ke cikin wannan rukunin haɗarin sun haɗa da ɗakunan keɓewa don waɗanda aka san ko ake zargin suna da COVID-19, gami da lokacin da ake aiwatar da hanyoyin samar da aerosol.
Ana iya amfani da iska mai matsi mai matsi mai matsi a wasu wuraren kiwon lafiya da kuma wuraren shakatawa.
Ya kamata a kula da samfurori bisa matakin tsaro na 3 na biosafety.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta ba da shawarar ware masu zuwa a cikin yankunan jira na musamman bisa la'akari da ko ana zargin suna da COVID-19. OSHA ta ba da shawarar respirators ban da sauran PPE ga mutanen da aka sani ko ake zargin suna da SARS-CoV-2 a cikin ƙafa 6 na aiki da kuma mutanen da ke aiwatar da hanyoyin samar da aerosol.
A cikin Amurka, N95 ko ingantaccen mai numfashi na numfashi na NOSH dole ne a yi amfani da shi a cikin tsarin ingantaccen tsarin kiyaye numfashi, wanda ya haɗa da gwajin lafiya, horo da gwaji na likita.
Sauran nau'ikan masu numfashi na iya samar da ƙarin kariya da haɓaka kwanciyar hankali ga ma'aikata. WHO ba ta ba da shawarar ɗaukar hoto ba, saboda COVID-19 ba ya yaduwa ta hanyar ruwan jiki, amma cutar ne ta numfashi.
WHO ta ba da shawarar sanya abin rufe fuska na tiyata ga ma'aikatan tantancewa a ƙofar shiga kawai.
WHO ta ba da shawarar sanya abin rufe fuska, tabarau, ko garkuwa, tufafi da safar hannu ga waɗanda ke tattara, kula ko jigilar samfuran numfashi daga marasa lafiya na COVID-19 ba tare da wata hanyar samar da aerosol ba.
Idan an yi aikin samar da aerosol, ana maye gurbin abin rufe fuska tare da N95 ko FFP2 respirator.
Ganin cewa samar da PPE bai isa ba a duniya, WHO ta ba da shawarar yin amfani da tazarar jiki kamar telemedicine, windows masu haske, da kuma barin waɗanda ke cikin kulawa kai tsaye su shiga ɗakin da ke da mai cutar COVID-19, amfani da PPE kawai don takamaiman aiki, ci gaba da amfani da shi ba tare da cire mai numfashi ba yayin kula da marasa lafiya da yawa da ke da cutar iri ɗaya, ba da izinin saka idanu da daidaita sarkar samar da PPE, da kuma hana sanya abin rufe fuska ga mutanen da ba su da alamun cutar.
