ACE2 yana ware carboxyl-terminal amino acid phenylalanine (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) daga angiotensin II kuma yana hydrolysing shi zuwa vasodilator angiotensin (1-7) (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 na iya ware wasu peptides, ciki har da [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dinorphine A, da ghrelin.
